title: Sunkost Gunerius
description: A health food store stocking a wide range of vegan products including meat substitutes, tofu, sausages, burgers, pizzas, ready-to-eat meals, spreads, plant milks and more. As of April 2013, only place in town where you can buy Vegusto and Jeezini vegan cheese in-store. Also stocks vegan snacks, chocolates, candy, juices, drinks, spices, tea, nuts, seeds, grains, dried goods and cosmetics. Facebook page is updated frequently with new vegan products. Brands include Fry's, Linda McCartney Foods, Amy's Kitchen, Viana, Redwood, Taifun, Just Wholefoods, Provamel, Oatly, Tartex, Cosmoveda and more. Has an online shop also.
